@notice Adds user account.

devdoc.author: Joby Augustine
devdoc.details: The main Bank contract for banking operations.

params._approve: `true` value indicates the approval and `false` indicates rejection.

params._cancelLoanId: id of the loan to be cancelled.

params._reserveBalance: Reserve balance that is to be maintained in the contract.

deadLineCrossed(uint256).details: Change Loan status to deadline crossed.

depositEthToBank().details: Owner deposits Eth to the Bank.

fixedDeposit(uint256).details: User deposits an amount for a fixed duration.

getAllUsers().details: Manager can get addresses of all Users

getFDDurationAndInterest(uint256,uint256.details: Get all fixed deposit durations and their interest rates.

params._count: Number of tariff that is to be fetched from  fdTariffToInfo array. In order to fetch entire array, set count to zero or a number higher than the last index of the array.
params._cursor: Starting value of the index that is to be fetched from fdTariffToInfo array.

getLoanDurationAndInterest(uint256,uint2.details: Get all loan durations and their interest rates.

params._count: Number of tariff that is to be fetched from  lnTariffToInfo array. In order to fetch entire array, set count to zero or a number higher than the last index of the array.
params._cursor: Starting value of the index that is to be fetched from lnTariffToInfo array.

getUserDepositDetails().details: Get the deposit details of an user.

getUserFdDetails(uint256,uint256).details: Get the fixed deposit details of an user.

params._count: Number of fd status that is to be fetched from user's fdInfo array. In order to fetch entire array, set count to zero or a number higher than the last index of the array.
params._cursor: Starting value of the index that is to be fetched from user's fdInfo array.

getUserLoanDetails(uint256,uint256).details: Get the loan details of an user.

params._count: Number of loan status that is to be fetched from user's loanInfo array. In order to fetch entire array, set count to zero or a number higher than the last index of the array.
params._cursor: Starting value of the index that is to be fetched from user's loanInfo array.

params._amount: Amount that is to be increased.

returns._0: true if `msg.sender` is the owner of the contract.

removeFDDurationAndInterest(uint256).details: Owner remove a fixed deposit duration and its interest rate.

removeLoanDurationAndInterest(uint256).details: Owner remove a loan duration and its interest rate.

renounceOwnership().details: Allows the current owner to relinquish control of the contract.

setFDDurationAndInterest(uint256,uint256.details: Owner sets fixed deposit duration and its interest rate

setLoanDurationAndInterest(uint256,uint2.details: Owner sets a loan duration and its interest rate.

transferOwnership(address).details: Allows the current owner to transfer control of the contract to a newOwner.

params.newOwner: The address to transfer ownership to.

viewLoanRequests(uint256,uint256).details: Manager can view all loan requests waiting for approval.

params._count: Number of loan requests that is to be fetched from the array. In order to fetch entire array, set count to zero or a number higher than the last index of the array.
params._cursor: Starting value of the index that is to be fetched from loanIdsOfPendingRequests array.

withdrawFD(uint256).details: User withdraws his/her fixed deposit with interest.

params._fdIndex: Index of the Fixed deposit to be withdrawn.

withdrawFDBeforeMaturity(uint256).details: User withdraws his/her fixed deposit before maturity period with penality of 5 percent of the FD Interest.

params._fdIndex: Index of the Fixed deposit to be withdrawn.

devdoc.title: Decentralized Bank

deadLineCrossed(uint256).notice: Change Loan status to deadline crossed.

deposit().notice: Send eth to deposit it in the account.

fixedDeposit(uint256).notice: Send fixed deposit amount in Eth and choose a tariff.

getAllUsers().notice: Manager can get addresses of all Users.

getFDDurationAndInterest(uint256,uint256.notice: Get all fixed deposit durations and their interest rates.

getLoanDurationAndInterest(uint256,uint2.notice: Get all loan durations and their interest rates

getUserDepositDetails().notice: Get the deposit details of an user.

getUserFdDetails(uint256,uint256).notice: Get the fixed deposit details of an user.

getUserLoanDetails(uint256,uint256).notice: Get the loan details of an user.

increaseReserveBalance(uint256).notice: Owner can increase the reserve balance that is to be maintained in the contract.

removeFDDurationAndInterest(uint256).notice: Owner can remove a fixed deposit duration and its interest rate.

removeLoanDurationAndInterest(uint256).notice: Owner can remove a loan duration and its interest rate.

renounceOwnership().notice: Renouncing to ownership will leave the contract without an owner. It will not be possible to call the functions with the `onlyOwner` modifier anymore.

setFDDurationAndInterest(uint256,uint256.notice: Owner sets fixed deposit duration and its interest rate.

setLoanDurationAndInterest(uint256,uint2.notice: Set a loan duration and its interest rate.

withdrawFDBeforeMaturity(uint256).notice: Withdraw fixed deposit before maturity period.
